description: This is a market group over what Donald J. Trump will say during his rally in Detroit, Michigan scheduled for October 18, 2024.

markets.description:
Donald Trump has scheduled a rally on October 18 in Detroit, Michigan (see: https://event.donaldjtrump.com/events/president-donald-j-trump-to-hold-a-rally-in-detroit-mi).

This market will resolve to "Yes" if Trump says "border" 25 or more times during their appearance at this event. Otherwise, the market will resolve to "No".

Any usage of the term regardless of context will count toward the resolution of this market.

Pluralization/possessive of the term will count toward the resolution of this market, however other forms will NOT count.

Compound words will count as long as "border" is part of the compound word and references the meaning which refers to a political boundary between nations.

If this candidate does not appear at this event, or if the event is otherwise cancelled or delayed beyond October 18, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source will be the video of the event.
